current
-------
+ major drupal-mode (based on php-mode)
+ move to improved php-mode (https://github.com/ejmr/php-mode)
* snippets for yasnippet
* flymake for php
* improved code for flymake integration from https://github.com/illusori/emacs-flymake
* PHP_CodeSniffer with flymake

for 2.x
-------
- projects support
- rfringe for flymake
- php & drupal docs parsing
- js2-mode for JavaScript https://github.com/mooz/js2-mode
- Drupal IDE cheatsheet

far future
----------
- installer
- cedet/semantic hooks/funcs/classes browsing (cedet/ecb?)
- recipe for el-get
- remote debugger (geben)
- more doxygen integration
- yas-jit for yasnippet fast loading
- MuMaMo for drupal, php and js modes
